raethecho.github.io/wiki/blog/2023/12/31/wiki-blog-example/", "title": "wiki blog example", "content_html": "<h1>Happy new years eve!</h1>\n<p>We hope you are all having fun and wish you all the best for the new year!</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-04-19T10:43:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/", "title": "This is my Notes about computer", "content_html": "<h1>This is my Notes about computer</h1>\n<p>Concludes linux, software, latex, etc</p>\n<h2>softwares</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/code/nvim\">neovim</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>linux</h2>\n<h2>[cheat sheets](/wiki/code/c...</h2>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-04-19T10:43:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/3in1wiki/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/3in1wiki/", "title": "\u7528mkdocs\u3001obsidian\u3001zotero\u642d\u5efa\u5728\u7ebf\u6587\u732e\u5b66\u4e60\u7b14\u8bb0", "content_html": "<h1>\u4f7f\u7528mkdocs\u3001obsidian\u3001zotero\u642d\u5efa\u5728\u7ebf\u6587\u732e\u5b66\u4e60\u7b14\u8bb0</h1>\n<p>\u5de5\u4f5c\u6d41\u662f\uff0c\u5728zotero\u4e2d\u9605\u8bfb\u548c\u6807\u8bb0\u3002\u7528zotero-better-notes\u63d2\u4ef6\u628a\u6807\u8bb0\u53d8\u6210\u6587\u672c\u683c\u5f0f\uff0c\u5e76\u4e14\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230obsidian\u7684\u5e93\u6587\u4ef6\u4e2d\uff0c\u8fdb\u4e00\u6b65\u7f16\u8f91\uff08\u6216\u8005\u7528nvim\u7f16\u8f91\uff09\u3002\u5728obsidian\u4e2d\u66f4\u65b9\u4fbf\u7b14\u8bb0\u94fe\u63a5\u8df3\u8f6c\uff0czotero\u53ea\u662f\u6587\u732e\u7ba1\u7406...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-04-19T10:43:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["second_brain"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/blogs/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/blogs/", "title": "\u7528obsidian\u7ba1\u7406\u591a\u4e2a\u535a\u5ba2", "content_html": "<h1>\u7528obsidian\u7ba1\u7406\u591a\u4e2a\u535a\u5ba2</h1>\n<p>\u4e00\u4e9b\u82b1\u91cc\u80e1\u54e8\u7684\u6280\u5de7\u3002</p>\n<h2>\u76ee\u6807</h2>\n<p>\u591a\u4e2a\u535a\u5ba2\u7f51\u7ad9\uff0c\u90fd\u7528github pages\u529f\u80fd\u53d1\u5e03\u3002\u591a\u4e2a\u535a\u5ba2\u7684post\u6587\u4ef6\u653e\u5728\u4e00\u4e2aobsidian\u4ed3\u5e93\u4e2d\u7ba1\u7406\uff0c\u5e76\u4e14\u672c\u8eab\u4f5c\u4e3a\u4e00\u4e2agithub repository\u3002push \u8fd9\u4e2aobsidian/github\u4ed3\u5e93\u540e\u5c06\u535a\u5ba2\u5185\u5bb9\u540c\u6b65\u5230\u5176\u4ed6\u535a\u5ba2r...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-04-19T10:43:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/keyboard/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/keyboard/", "title": "\u952e\u76d8\u548c\u56fa\u4ef6", "content_html": "<h1>\u952e\u76d8\u786c\u4ef6\u56fa\u4ef6</h1>\n<p>\u5b9e\u73b0\u6539\u952e\u7684\u975e\u8f6f\u4ef6\u65b9\u6cd5</p>\n<h2>pros and cons</h2>\n<h2>qmk</h2>\n<h2>zmk</h2>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-04-19T10:43:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["linux"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/nvim/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/nvim/", "title": "My Neovim Config", "content_html": "<h1>My neovim</h1>\n<p>My <a href=\"https://github.com/HiraethEcho/nvim\">config</a> on github.</p>\n<p>I'm using nvim as a code editor, mainly for latex and markdown.</p>\n<h2>Usage</h2>\n<h3>gener...</h3>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-04-19T10:43:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["arch", "code"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/obsidian/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/obsidian/", "title": "obsidian", "content_html": "<h1>obsidian</h1>\n<h2>Install</h2>\n<h2>plugins</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>dataview (display files by metadata)</li>\n<li>kanban (plan things, especially something with many stages)</li>\n<li>Hover Editor (actua...</li>\n</ul>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-04-19T10:43:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["obsidian", "second_brain"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/ssh/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/ssh/", "title": "About ssh", "content_html": "<h1>ssh</h1>\n<h2>\u5185\u7f51ssh\u8fde\u63a5</h2>\n<p>\u4e00\u4e2aipv6\u5730\u5740\u7684\u7535\u8111\uff0c\u4f5c\u4e3a\u4e2d\u95f4\u673a\uff0c\u4e00\u4e2a\u5185\u7f51\u7684\u7535\u8111\uff0c\u8bb0\u4f5c\u670d\u52a1\u673a\uff0c\u671f\u671b\u5176\u4ed6\u7684\u5ba2\u6237\u673a\uff08\u6bd4\u5982iphone\uff09\u8fde\u63a5\u5230\u5185\u7f51\u7684\u670d\u52a1\u673a\u3002</p>\n<h3>\u601d\u8def</h3>\n<p>\u5c06\u670d\u52a1\u673a\u7684ssh\u7aef\u53e3\u8f6c\u53d1\u5230\u4e2d\u95f4\u673a\u7684\u7aef\u53e3\uff0c\u5373\u6570\u636e\u4ece\u4e2d\u95f4\u673a\u7684\u7aef\u53e3\u4f20\u9001\u5230\u670d\u52a1\u673a\uff1b\u5ba2\u6237\u673a\u8fde\u63a5\u4e2d\u95f4\u673a\u7684\u7aef\u53e3\u5373\u53ef\u3002\u4e2d\u95f4\u673a\u6709ipv6\u5730\u5740\uff0c\u5c31\u53ef\u4ee5ssh...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-04-19T10:43:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/sync/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/sync/", "title": "\u5404\u79cd\u540c\u6b65\u65b9\u6cd5", "content_html": "<h1>\u5404\u79cd\u540c\u6b65\u65b9\u6cd5</h1>\n<h2>\u4e91\u540c\u6b65</h2>\n<h3>\u4e91\u76d8</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>koofr</li>\n<li>onedrive</li>\n<li>ali</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>\u6587\u4ef6\u540c\u6b65\u65b9\u6cd5</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>webdav</li>\n<li>rclone</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>\u7ba1\u7406</h3>\n<p>alist</p>\n<h2>\u672c\u5730</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>unison</li>\n</ul>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-04-19T10:43:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["linux", "second_brain"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/windows/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/windows/", "title": "Windows\u91cd\u88c5\u6307\u5357", "content_html": "<h1>Windows\u91cd\u88c5\u6307\u5357</h1>\n<p>\u8bb0\u5f55\u4e00\u4e0b\u91cd\u88c5\u6216\u8005\u7b2c\u4e00\u6b21\u5b89\u88c5windows\u7684\u4e00\u4e9b\u6ce8\u610f\u4e8b\u9879\u3002</p>\n<h2>\u91cd\u88c5</h2>\n<p>\u6309<kbd>windows</kbd>\u7136\u540e\u6309\u4f4f<kbd>shift</kbd>\u70b9\u51fb\u91cd\u542f\uff0c\u8fd9\u6837\u91cd\u542f\u540e\u4f1a\u8fdb\u5165\u6062\u590d\u6a21\u5f0f\uff08\u4e4b\u7c7b\u7684\uff09\uff0c\u8fd9\u91cc\u53ef\u4ee5\u9009\u62e9\u91cd\u88c5\u7cfb\u7edf\u3002\u6216\u8005\u5728\u8bbe\u7f6e\u4e2d\u7684\u7cfb\u7edf\u6062\u590d\u90e8\u5206\u3002<br>\n\u91cd\u88c5\u7cfb\u7edf\u53ea\u91cd\u88c5C\u76d8\uff0c\u5176\u4ed6\u76d8\u662f\u4e0d...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-04-19T10:43:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/zotero/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/zotero/", "title": "zotero", "content_html": "<h1>Zotero</h1>\n<h2>Install and basic setting</h2>\n<h2>Plugins</h2>\n<p><strong>zotero 7:</strong>\n- zotmoov\n- zotero better notes</p>\n<h2>Sync</h2>\n<p>using ~~zotmoov~~ attanger to move files</p>\n<p>zotero ...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-04-19T10:43:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["second_brain"]}]}